      <title>新西兰航空暂停奥克兰至芝加哥直飞服务</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/air-new-zealand-pauses-auckland-chicago-non-stop-service-2024-03-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰航空周二表示，由于劳斯莱斯遄达 1000 发动机的可用性持续面临挑战，计划于今年 3 月 31 日至 10 月 25 日暂停奥克兰至芝加哥的直飞航班。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/air-new-zealand-pauses-auckland-chicago-non-stop-service-2024-03-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 23:15:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通戴蒙敦促美联储等到六月之后再降息</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/jpmorgans-dimon-urges-us-fed-wait-past-june-before-cutting-rates-2024-03-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通首席执行官杰米·戴蒙(Jamie Dimon)周二敦促美联储等到6月之后再降息，认为央行需要增强其抗击通胀的信誉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/jpmorgans-dimon-urges-us-fed-wait-past-june-before-cutting-rates-2024-03-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 22:49:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜代表团罕见会见蒙古总统 - 朝中社</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korean-delegation-meets-mongolian-president-rare-visit-kcna-2024-03-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜官方媒体朝中社称，朝鲜外交部副部长朴明浩周一会见了蒙古国总统呼日勒苏赫，这是这个孤立国家的外交代表团罕见的出访。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korean-delegation-meets-mongolian-president-rare-visit-kcna-2024-03-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 22:14:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦前财政部长伊沙克·达尔出任外交部长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistans-former-finance-chief-takes-up-role-foreign-minister-2024-03-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦前财政部长伊沙克·达尔周一被任命为该国外交部长，目前日益严峻的经济和安全挑战将主导该国的外交政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistans-former-finance-chief-takes-up-role-foreign-minister-2024-03-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 18:46:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦最大银行首席执行官被选带领国家走出经济危机</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/ceo-pakistans-largest-bank-picked-lead-country-out-economic-crisis-2024-03-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[被总理谢巴兹·谢里夫任命为巴基斯坦财政部长的穆罕默德·奥朗则布是一位经验丰富的私人银行家，也是该国薪酬最高的高管之一，但此前从未担任过公职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/ceo-pakistans-largest-bank-picked-lead-country-out-economic-crisis-2024-03-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 18:23:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塔斯社称，俄罗斯以间谍罪逮捕韩国男子</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-arrests-south-korean-man-spying-tass-says-2024-03-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯国家通讯社塔斯社周一报道称，一名韩国公民因涉嫌间谍活动在俄罗斯被捕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-arrests-south-korean-man-spying-tass-says-2024-03-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 14:06:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度在选举前实施遭到穆斯林反对的公民法</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-moves-implement-citizenship-law-opposed-by-muslims-weeks-before-election-2024-03-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度周一采取行动，实施了 2019 年公民法，该法被批评为歧视穆斯林，几周后，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪 (Narendra Modi) 将为印度教民族主义政府寻求罕见的第三个任期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-moves-implement-citizenship-law-opposed-by-muslims-weeks-before-election-2024-03-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 12:47:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚洪水、山体滑坡已造成 26 人死亡，至少 6 人失踪</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/floods-landslides-kill-26-indonesia-least-six-missing-2024-03-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当局周一表示，印度尼西亚西苏门答腊省的洪水和山体滑坡已造成 26 人死亡，至少 6 人失踪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/floods-landslides-kill-26-indonesia-least-six-missing-2024-03-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 11:49:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>另一艘中国科考船在印度附近被发现，引发不安</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/another-chinese-research-vessel-spotted-off-india-fuelling-unease-2024-03-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两个月内第二艘中国科考船在印度海岸附近被发现，这加剧了新德里对其可能在其后院收集军事情报的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/another-chinese-research-vessel-spotted-off-india-fuelling-unease-2024-03-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 10:33:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜副外相罕见访问蒙古</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-vice-foreign-minister-mongolia-rare-visit-2024-03-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[蒙古外交部表示，朝鲜外交部副部长朴明浩周一在蒙古与阿马图夫辛·贡博苏伦举行会谈，这是朝鲜外交代表团罕见的出访。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-vice-foreign-minister-mongolia-rare-visit-2024-03-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 09:20:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
